                            <button type="submit" id="submitBtn" class="flex-1 sm:flex-none px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-indigo-700 transition-all transform hover:scale-105 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg font-semibold"><i class="fas fa-save mr-2"></i>‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏∂‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•</button>
